  note         = {Proves that KNN walk over the vindex and dense matrix multiply produce identical predictions at every layer boundary (L0--L34, Gemma~3 4B). Walk is faster than dense (517ms vs 535ms). Source-confirmed by local repository inspection (2026-07-01).}
}

